{"tid":867624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中国矽谷崛起] 北京注資200億 救高科技業流動性","createTime":"2018-10-18T23:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T13:37:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d52441d5af347f9678643a11f97e103d5a2069","tid":867624,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:44:35.000Z","msg":"北京注資200億 救高科技業流動性<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%B3%A8%E8%B3%87200%E5%84%84-%E6%95%91%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A5%AD%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7-215009899--finance.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E8%25B3%2587200%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%2595%2591%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2580%25A7-215009899--finance.html&d=USo9LOJMBp8EuMlQhn0d75ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=af9f87ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%B3%A8%E8%B3%87200%E5%84%84-%E6%95%91%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%A5%AD%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7-215009899--finance.html</a><br />\n<br />\n工商時報【楊日興╱綜合報導】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在日前深圳拿出數百億元人民幣（下同）入市扶持當地上市公司後，不少大陸地方政府紛紛跟進發布相關政策。向來有「中國矽谷」稱號的北京市海淀區為扶持當地科技公司度過流動性難關，成立100億元基金，昨（18）日也傳出北京市政府將加碼該基金至多200％，並鼓勵其他轄區複製該模式。</span><br />\n<br />\n北京證監局16日發布，海淀區國資和東興證券共同發起規模100億元的基金，以幫助當地遇到資金困難的民營科技企業，並化解海淀區股票質押風險。中國證券報昨引述知情人士說法稱，北京市政府有意在海淀百億基金的基礎上，再配100％至200％的資金給予支持，意謂該檔基金最高規模可達300億元。<br />\n<br />\n在大陸各地方救市行動中，廣東省是國資入股民企數量最多、出手最頻繁之地，省內各地相關政策接連發布，在深圳宣布百億元專項資金之後，佛山市順德區也表示，將安排專項資金效仿深圳模式，改善當地上市公司流動性。相較北京扶持當地科技企業，近日廣東銀監局則推出12條政策，著眼外貿企業的穩定發展。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除了廣東、北京，杭州近日也傳出，已在9月上旬著手計劃，未來可能透過低息甚至無息貸款，或是國有資本直接持股等方式扶持杭州的上市企業。</span><br />\n<br />\n全部變曬国企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df004c25996eeab5f39b7931430e33d9a78b5eb","tid":867624,"uid":62646,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔係有錢就有創新科技既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個無思想自由的地方何來創新"},{"pid":"4878d0d78e809dcbbeab1f393aa782bba27a2b07","tid":867624,"uid":170044,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:05:15.000Z","msg":"偷人技術 禁止國外企業對手公平競爭<br />\n垃圾支那狗 注幾多錢你地都係一班農民黎架咋"},{"pid":"253ea6c20baf638eb1da3d0214f69a41c742d59c","tid":867624,"uid":88841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"個波愈吹愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bed9a62adcd02ce2859a62e0c9f6b3ab89efa7e","tid":867624,"uid":5715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"又有得貪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fb18f314bba58805ec2a4db0546c43f7f591a1","tid":867624,"uid":21707,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"200億有幾多呀？<br />\n<br />\n香港個創科局貪咗成500億啦. 咪又係黃豆都唔會有粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0706e950c8432751c098ed6838fdfe9001d6c07","tid":867624,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"錢又係香港來"},{"pid":"a5417cbb2c74081593f5f6d23b5a07bc4ba1ffb9","tid":867624,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T01:27:39.000Z","msg":"印個新LOGO 攞幾億<br />\n<br />\n自煮研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2f151de591f4fc5ab1e679b4f4e8d48902a592","tid":867624,"uid":12554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"国進民退？<br />\n<br />\n有錢整基金但無錢還地方債？"},{"pid":"51126ca0ff46c23ea3f4dcc29f08ee84128f72ed","tid":867624,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor